  The MCP tool-generation pattern adapted in src/tools/generate.ts —
  declaring method + path + input schema once and deriving both the MCP tool
  registration and the HTTP dispatch from that single declaration — follows
  the route-registry approach of OpenShip's apps/api/src/modules/mcp/ module
  (mcp-tools.ts, mcp-dispatch.ts, mcp-server.ts). Only the design pattern was
  adapted; the implementation in this repository is original and specific to
  the Capix control plane. No OpenShip source code is vendored.
